.TH HYPRLAND\-SHARE\-PICKER 1 "2025-12-05" "xdg-desktop-portal-hyprland 1.3.11" "Hyprland Ecosystem"
.SH NAME
hyprland\-share\-picker \- screen share picker for xdg\-desktop\-portal\-hyprland
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hyprland\-share\-picker
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B hyprland\-share\-picker
is a Qt\-based screen share picker used by
.BR xdg\-desktop\-portal\-hyprland .
It is invoked automatically when an application requests screen sharing
through the XDG Desktop Portal, allowing users to select which window or
screen to share.
.PP
This utility is not typically invoked directly by users.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-allow\-token
Allow token by default for portal permissions.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B XDPH_WINDOW_SHARING_LIST
A formatted string of available windows for sharing, populated by
xdg\-desktop\-portal\-hyprland before invoking the picker.
.SH DEPENDENCIES
.BR slurp (1)
is required for region selection.
.BR qt6\-qtwayland
is required for Wayland integration.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR Hyprland (1)
.SH AUTHOR
The Hyprland Development Team
.SH BUGS
Report bugs at
.UR https://github.com/hyprwm/xdg-desktop-portal-hyprland/issues
.UE .
